high_descs: Turn right walk forward and turn left towards the counter
Grab a knife from the counter
Walk with the knife back to the other side of the counter
Slice the apple on the counter
Walk to the other side of the counter and towards the microwave
Put the knife on the counter next to the microwave
Walk to the counter next to the stools
Grab a slice of the apple
Walk with the slice of the apple towards the sink
Put the slice of the apple in the sink, open the water and close it
Walk the the slice of the apple towards the microwave
Put the slice of the apple next to the knife on the counter
anns.task_desc: Slice the apple, put it in the sink, fill with water, put it on the counter

high_descs: Turn to the left, walk around the counter top to face the knifes.
Pick up the knife on the right side.
Turn to the left, walk around the counter top.
Cut the apple by the square bowl.
Turn to the right walk around the counter top, walk forward.
Place the knife on the counter top to the left of the salt.
Turn around, walk around the counter top.
Pick up a slice of apple.
Turn right, walk to face the sink.
Place the apple in the sink on the right side towards the front. Turn on the water then turn off the water.
Pick up the apple from the sink.
Turn to the left, walk forward to face the counter top. Place the apple to the right of the knife on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Cut the apple, put the knife and slice of apple on the counter top.

high_descs: Turn right and go around the end of the peninsula to the other side of the peninsula.
Pick up the knife on the right.
Turn left and go back around to the other side of the peninsula.
Cut the apple into thirds that sits to the left of the bowl.
Turn right and go around the end of the peninsula and across the room to the dishwasher across the room.
Put the knife on the counter above the dishwasher with the blade pointing to the left.
Turn around and go around the end of the peninsula to the other side.
Pick up a third of the apple.
Turn right and go around the end of the island and across the room to the sink.
Wash the apple in the sink.
Move a few feet to the left.
Set the apple piece down on the counter to the right of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a piece of apple on the counter with the knife.
